WHO_IS_THIS_COURSE_FOR: A course for people with no previous experience in counselling training, but who have an interest in counselling or who want to use counselling skills in their work. Practical training in interpersonal and counselling skills, an exploration of professional issues like counselling ethics, confidentiality, working with diversity, personal development and theory.
